content:
Fix:
修复国际服和日服课程表爱心数量识别问题
Fix the problem of recognizing the number of love hearts in international and Japanese service schedule

修复更新api遇阻时导致GUI进程无响应问题
Fix the problem of unresponsive GUI process when updating api is blocked

修复日服推图遇到等级过高提示会退出推图任务问题
Fix the problem of quitting quests in Japanese service when encountering the prompt of too high level in push map.

修复关卡所需票卷或体力不足时的弹窗识别异常问题
Fix the problem of pop-up windows recognizing anomalies when there are not enough Ticket Rolls or Stamina required for a level.
